It's a little harder to follow with this three-state variable.
So the idea is that it fails the decision only when the OPTIONAL are the only plugins in the stack?
If so, the original structure may stay it was (except the OPTIONAL else-if) and here you could do
if(optionalFailure && getStack().stream().filter(Predicate::not(AuthorizationEntity::isOptional)).findAny().isEmpty()) {
  return optionalFailure;
}

